=============================================
HABANERO-C++ LIBRARY INSTALLATION PROCEDURE
=============================================

1) Checkout hclib repository:

git clone https://github.com/habanero-rice/hclib.git

2) Checkout ocr repository:

git clone https://github.com/01org/ocr.git

3) Set the paths correctly in ./scripts/setMeFirst.sh (bash) or ./scripts/setMeFirst.csh (cshell)

4) cd scripts

5) source ./setMeFirst.sh (or source ./setMeFirst.csh)

6) cd ..

7) ./install.sh

=============================================
BUILDING TESTCASES
=============================================

1) Tests are inside "./test" 

2) Each testcase has its own Makefile. Simply use "make" to build testcases

=============================================
EXECUTING TESTCASES
=============================================

1) Directory "machine-configs" contains various OCR worker configuration files

2) For using "10" work-stealing worker threads, do:
export OCR_CONFIG=<ABSOLUTE PATH TO THE CONFIGURATION FILE>/mach-hcpp-10w.cfg
              OR
setenv OCR_CONFIG <ABSOLUTE PATH TO THE CONFIGURATION FILE>/mach-hcpp-10w.cfg

3) Execute the testcase like normal c++ executable: ./a.out


